    <CMUI_Label name="lblBlurb" id="380e042b-125b-4578-943d-a25aee142852">
        <alignment>1</alignment>
        <caption>Screens like LOLO Planning and Yard Grid Areas draw cargo and draw icons to represent values on the graphic.  Because of limited space when displaying cargo graphically, typically only a subset of icons are ever shown.  This screen allows users to prioritise which icons are displayed.</caption>
